{"tid":1797472,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"特區政府反駁香港觀察的指控","createTime":"2019-12-25T12:37:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-26T04:50:00.000Z","uid":21470,"like":12,"dislike":226,"uniUserReply":87,"replies":[{"pid":"44915c52230b652d99d7fda101095baf602be08c","tid":1797472,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T12:37:05.000Z","msg":"政府反駁香港觀察指控<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n  特區政府發言人今日（十二月二十五日）強烈反駁香港觀察早前發表的聲明，該聲明指控香港警務處使用粗暴武力針對在尖沙咀及其他地區慶祝聖誕前夕的「和平購物人士和示威者」。<br />\n<br />\n  發言人強調：「這些錯誤指控和捏造完全與事實不符。警方在整個行動中，一直採取嚴謹而克制的態度，只用了最低武力應對聖誕前夕暴力示威者公然的違法行為，包括縱火、肆意破壞店鋪和滙豐銀行旺角分行、堵塞道路、破壞旺角一帶的21組交通燈、兇殘地攻擊無辜市民、用汽油彈襲擊警員、衝擊警方防線和非法集會。」<br />\n<br />\n  這些違法行為毫無疑問大大影響了公眾和平與安全，警方因此有必要採取執法行動。<br />\n<br />\n  就香港觀察主席指「香港目睹警察在聖誕前夕的暴行」，發言人形容有關言論是「虛構、完全不負責任及極度不公平」。<br />\n<br />\n  發言人補充：「我們必須杜絕這些錯誤看法和惡意謊言，因為它們向海外社會描繪了一個完全錯誤的香港形象。香港堅信並嚴格遵守法治。香港警察絕不可能向和平購物人士和示威者採取執法行動。」<br />\n <br />\n完<br />\n2019年12月25日（星期三）<br />\n香港時間19時51分<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n<br />\nHong Kong Watch 原文<br />\n<br />\nSTATEMENT: Hong Kong Watch Condemns Christmas Eve Police Brutality And Calls For Immediate International Independent Inquiry And Targeted Magnitsky Sanctions<br />\n<br />\nHong Kong Watch is appalled by the police brutality unleashed on peaceful shoppers and protesters celebrating Christmas Eve in Hong Kong earlier today.<br />\n<br />\nWidespread reports of beatings, firing rubber bullets at people&rsquo;s heads and faces (in clear breach of international norms), indiscriminate use of teargas and water cannon against largely peaceful crowds celebrating Christmas in Tsim Sha Tsui and other areas represent yet another example of the escalating human rights crisis in Hong Kong. <br />\n<br />\nIn horrific scenes, a protester chased by police fell from one level of a shopping mall to another and sustained very serious injuries while another fell from a rooftop after police shot at him multiple times as he clung to the edge.<br />\n<br />\nHong Kong Watch&rsquo;s co-founder and Chairman, Benedict Rogers, said: <br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;Hong Kong witnessed truly outrageous police brutality on Christmas Eve. Are Hong Kongers now not even allowed to gather to celebrate Christmas peacefully, to shop and sing carols? The level of violence in Hong Kong has reached such severe and sustained levels that an international, independent inquiry should be urgently established.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;We also call on the United Kingdom to lead the international community by establishing an international contact group of like-minded nations to co-ordinate a global policy response to the crisis. <br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;Furthermore, we urge the British Prime Minister to speak out clearly and urgently, and we call on the British government and others to introduce targeted Magnitsky sanctions against those responsible in Hong Kong and China for severe human rights violations, including officials in the government and the police. <br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;It is time for immediate international action to stop the crisis in Hong Kong escalating still further, to end impunity and to move towards peace and the re-establishment of Hong Kong&rsquo;s freedoms and autonomy.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hongkongwatch.org/all-posts/2019/12/24/statement-hong-kong-watch-condemns-christmas-eve-police-brutality-and-calls-for-immediate-international-independent-inquiry-and-targeted-magnitsky-sanctions?fbclid=IwAR2RC87PPDdouLqfPM-xIAR2L0ENJ9PCokkH7YQPeCJPj2IxWxb3DDYOkN0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hongkongwatch.org%2Fall-posts%2F2019%2F12%2F24%2Fstatement-hong-kong-watch-condemns-christmas-eve-police-brutality-and-calls-for-immediate-international-independent-inquiry-and-targeted-magnitsky-sanctions%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2RC87PPDdouLqfPM-xIAR2L0ENJ9PCokkH7YQPeCJPj2IxWxb3DDYOkN0&d=TvOq0m68uPCtaVYdNLQuFCvt59O44HeJS3%2BtxtDyp5g%3D&h=5e0e33b6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hongkongwatch.org/all-posts/2019/12/24/statement-hong-kong-watch-condemns-christmas-eve-police-brutality-and-calls-for-immediate-international-independent-inquiry-and-targeted-magnitsky-sanctions?fbclid=IwAR2RC87PPDdouLqfPM-xIAR2L0ENJ9PCokkH7YQPeCJPj2IxWxb3DDYOkN0</a>"},{"pid":"6ffa25f7d34fddc4cfbf5ca75bc219895d2d46e1","tid":1797472,"uid":93383,"like":72,"dislike":0,"score":72,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T12:37:56.000Z","msg":"香港政府你真係好樣衰呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adbee21f1d59acc769ea4ab5328746f10c0ec6c6","tid":1797472,"uid":168138,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T12:38:57.000Z","msg":"收皮啦"},{"pid":"f7c73f3a26780026ca56025c1bfbf49dd9d24d9b","tid":1797472,"uid":87780,"like":55,"dislike":0,"score":55,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T12:39:13.000Z","msg":"撐狗撐到咁心安理得就唔好理外國點睇啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d5ce42aad29bebf9b899c3eb1fe16b68d15c28f","tid":1797472,"uid":36178,"like":70,"dislike":2,"score":68,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T12:39:32.000Z","msg":"香港警察絕不可能向和平購物人士和示威者採取執法行動。」<br />\n???????????????????????"},{"pid":"0e760f9024be28fc6cea844a355388b7f2e13fad","tid":1797472,"uid":288304,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T12:41:19.000Z","msg":"放便衣狗入場引戰都叫考慮市民安全"},{"pid":"64d38ed09d0fbb6f332ada9efd19aabd174134e9","tid":1797472,"uid":5737,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"quote":{"pid":"7d5ce42aad29bebf9b899c3eb1fe16b68d15c28f","tid":1797472,"uid":36178,"like":70,"dislike":2,"score":68,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T12:39:32.000Z","msg":"香港警察絕不可能向和平購物人士和示威者採取執法行動。」<br />\n???????????????????????"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T12:43:18.000Z","msg":"人唔笑 狗都吠<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/angry.gif\" 