id":1797472,"uid":35087,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"45e30d3588b235dc7e1dffb402a3f473f111f7d1","tid":1797472,"uid":21470,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"c61b01ed6e0ebf58c20618f35a9c666da994572d","tid":1797472,"uid":14449,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T13:16:54.000Z","msg":"做咩今次會屌hong kong watch?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T13:25:18.000Z","msg":"因為Hong Kong Watch 月初提過BNO 平權，受中共留意，一有咩風足草動就出黎屌幾句"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T13:36:27.000Z","msg":"做到嘢 已認證<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其他gp請努力"},{"pid":"02abb450196d16fa43eaeedbb62dddf55130dc7c","tid":1797472,"uid":268186,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T13:36:34.000Z","msg":"政府承認香港觀察指控<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n特區政府發言人今日（十二月二十五日）承認香港觀察早前發表的聲明，該聲明指控香港警務處使用粗暴武力針對在尖沙咀及其他地區慶祝聖誕前夕的「和平購物人士和示威者」。<br />\n<br />\n發言人強調：「這些指控完全與事實相符。警方在整個行動中，一直採取有殺錯，無放過的態度，只用了最高武力應對聖誕前夕香港市民的消費行為，包括行商場、買禮物和食飯、過馬路、兇殘地攻擊便衣黑警、用汽油彈紅燒黑警、衝擊警方防線和合法集會。」<br />\n<br />\n這些合法行為毫無疑問大大刺激經濟，警方並無必要採取執法行動。<br />\n<br />\n就香港觀察主席指「香港目睹警察在聖誕前夕的暴行」，發言人形容有關言論是「真實、完全負責任及極度公平」。<br />\n<br />\n發言人補充：「我們必須杜絕中囯錯誤看法和惡意謊言，因為它們向海外社會描繪了一個完全錯誤的香港形象。香港示威者堅信並嚴格遵守法治。香港公安曾向和平購物人士和示威者採取非法行動。」<br />\n<br />\n完<br />\n2019年12月25日（星期三）<br />\n香港時間19時51分"},{"pid":"04d61670310cc93b02fa09de7b53c75f4ddb4078","tid":1797472,"uid":53003,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T13:36:52.000Z","msg":"這些錯誤指控和捏造完全與事實不符。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n外交部啲發言template 嚟？"},{"pid":"88e42b9d4354d162812880899874861cf51c5859","tid":1797472,"uid":7327,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T13:37:20.000Z","msg":"為左果3萬隻狗<br />\n輸左形象<br />\n輸左經濟<br />\n輸左區議會<br />\n準備輸埋立法會<br />\n高官仲要準備比人制裁<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n高官們 建制派 商家佬 <br />\n你地真係覺得值？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"749923974b8edbbe227a21350b1ff1335b5a6655","tid":1797472,"uid":57480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T13:37:29.000Z","msg":"pull"},{"pid":"998a5bff6ccc89126560d1ac48d0d360f97f57ad","tid":1797472,"uid":73915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T13:38:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e66bac62a60be78fbe260d2354693a94e386474c","tid":1797472,"uid":442,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"88e42b9d4354d162812880899874861cf51c5859","tid":1797472,"uid":7327,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T13:37:20.000Z","msg":"為左果3萬隻狗<br />\n輸左形象<br />\n輸左經濟<br />\n輸左區議會<br />\n準備輸埋立法會<br />\n高官仲要準備比人制裁<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n高官們 建制派 商家佬 <br />\n你地真係覺得值？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T13:39:47.000Z","msg":"唔值都要跪<br />\n根本係黨衛軍"},{"pid":"03b82fb95bc3a902dac20dab8f03b87eaa8e2f93","tid":1797472,"uid":91821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T13:41:55.000Z","msg":"謊言黎講，邊個最專業，大家都知"},{"pid":"359d106e9d8919e4e6109ba9f8b4b8eebaa5b0a0","tid":1797472,"uid":269202,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T13:42:07.000Z","msg":"其實有612，721，831仲憑乜野話人不實報導？"},{"pid":"7a7efc6b63dc9c8c981a67d73372f484b07b41d0","tid":1797472,"uid":322405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T13:44:00.000Z","msg":"屌"},{"pid":"a65c837087117bb00e313afaf3b81da936d2bb07","tid":1797472,"uid":161365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T13:44:49.000Z","msg":"呢個政府都代表唔到香港人 區議員聯署譴責警暴就有用啦"},{"pid":"3ee015e06f55e8b64398bab